{"tid":338043,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人太鍾意散播失敗主義","createTime":"2017-07-27T23:48:02.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-28T04:52:33.000Z","uid":41245,"like":280,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"30dde4e48fcf2b04d543a590adc0c0d8b1386b95","tid":338043,"uid":41245,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T23:48:02.000Z","msg":"網上言論有好高嘅政治價值<br />\n一個留言效果媲美傳媒一個標題<br />\n甚至更大<br />\n所以唔該大家清楚自己發言<strong>想達到咩效果</strong>同<strong>實際達到咩效果</strong><br />\n失敗主義係有<strong>百分百</strong>挫民運士氣嘅效果，無論你點解釋<br />\n<br />\n所以散播失敗主義嘅，你地嘅行為達到嘅效果根本同維穩冇分別<br />\n<br />\n你地自問下，你講失敗主義言論「香港冇得救」「港豬唔理」嘅心態係咩？失望？灰心？wfc，無論你原因係咩，你做嘅都係<strong>同維穩冇分別</strong>"},{"pid":"6f6b4a863c14f7b64daee82c81f6988984884a4f","tid":338043,"uid":106430,"like":5,"dislike":5,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T23:50:02.000Z","msg":"少有高汁Post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84d54eedcdadadfff4e28a5e06675948c3232b11","tid":338043,"uid":6778,"like":5,"dislike":14,"score":-9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T23:53:07.000Z","msg":"咁香港人係失敗去呀  唔係你想點?"},{"pid":"6e5b7091f493e22fabedd9c8d611e6663cba8e53","tid":338043,"uid":6778,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T23:53:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁香港人係失敗<span style=\"color: red;\">開</span>呀  唔係你想點?</blockquote>"},{"pid":"d0f6e7f8e461f69ff0cb52e044ba72013b5c6bef","tid":338043,"uid":50327,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T00:00:06.000Z","msg":"樓主唔記得左班港豬唱完今天我，階段性勝利果d事蹟？"},{"pid":"014ceaf0341ba2dd3119f5e3a0a516ba723d63e4","tid":338043,"uid":78574,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T00:14:48.000Z","msg":"咁你散播下正能量囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c6955b894095a546ef604770e93f2e3b36adc24","tid":338043,"uid":38523,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T00:20:33.000Z","msg":"個班真係香港先算啦"},{"pid":"0ede30b66194993a1eda2f0cc38131e4b2ab7bdd","tid":338