到而家既政治現實，而的確可以話無乜出路，如果有幸讀書比較多，我諗大家目光要放遠一啲，爭取背後係實踐價值，呢啲價值係咩、到底有幾重要，係唔係無可能、短時間做唔到終極目標可以做咩呢，係唔係做其他既嘢就無意思呢"},{"pid":"922cc7e5c908295801d2e284a2a3cb21e4a6b5d3","tid":338043,"uid":25327,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T23:59:33.000Z","msg":"明知唔得既仲要推人去死？"},{"pid":"3a2407e39c0c2ad5af11e044c860dac35e13ea5c","tid":338043,"uid":34543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T00:43:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>明知唔得既仲要推人去死？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n知其不可而為之，有啲嘢唔可以計成唔成功，而係應唔應該，值唔值得去做"},{"pid":"1223ebea0aa812fadfb243c3827b15f4dc25a6c2","tid":338043,"uid":33999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T01:17:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>明知唔得既仲要推人去死？</blockquote><br />\n唔好同人講你反抗政府<br />\n我怕失禮"},{"pid":"3dabc37596096a52ecc1350d47a685901443b57f","tid":338043,"uid":25327,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T04:38:48.000Z","msg":"講咁多咪又係唔得，唔係你地坐監梗係係度話值唔值得應唔應該啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"414704f9db5887c652da95111cd3dcb880a132d3","tid":338043,"uid":25327,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T04:44:02.000Z","msg":"佢地三個出返黎都依然咁盡心盡力搞既話咁就有說服力喇，家下你地講乜都假<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，革命要犧牲，坐係電腦面前講咩失敗主義亳無說服力，如果黃豬鋒就唔同，人地真係受緊成件即刻岩曬，由你地把口你地講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}